      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>新疆香瓜子葵花子春节特惠</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #D0021B;\n            --accent-color: #FFD700;\n            --bg-color: #FAF3E0;\n            --text-color: #333;\n            --max-width: 800px;\n        }\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: var(--max-width);\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n        h1, h2, h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        section, footer {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .price-highlight {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 600px) {\n            body {\n                font-size: 0.95rem;\n            }\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 1.5rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"hero-section\">\n            <h1>春节盛宴，新疆香瓜子葵花子，香脆好味道</h1>\n            <p>限时优惠，节日囤货首选，高性价比美味享不停</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"price-box\">\n            <h2>现价 ￥29.9 元 原价 ￥49.9 元</h2>\n            <p class=\"price-highlight\">使用优惠券后仅 ￥24.9 元</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"promo-countdown\">\n            <h3>限时促销倒计时</h3>\n            <p>剩余 2 天 5 小时，库存不足 500 件，请及时抢购</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"coupon-center\">\n            <h3>优惠券中心</h3>\n            <p>领取满 50 减 10 元、满 100 减 25 元等多种优惠券</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"cart-module\">\n            <h3>购物车加购</h3>\n            <p>选择数量后立即加入购物车，享受春节包邮服务</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"sales-ticker\">\n            <h3>实时销量</h3>\n            <p>已有 3254 位顾客完成下单，热销不停</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"product-specs\">\n            <h3>产品规格</h3>\n            <p>产地：新疆<br>品牌：阳光葵花<br>净含量：500g/袋</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"reviews-section\">\n            <h3>用户评价</h3>\n            <p>评分：4.8 分，用户一致好评，香脆可口，颗粒饱满</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"details-toggle\">\n            <h3>详细介绍</h3>\n            <p>源自新疆优质葵花田，结合传统烘焙工艺，配料表简单纯粹</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"recommendations\">\n            <h3>相似产品推荐</h3>\n            <p>葵花籽混合礼盒、瓜子礼品包装，让春节送礼更贴心</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"innovation-luckybag\">\n            <h3>春节福袋互动</h3>\n            <p>参与福袋抽奖，赢取免单与限量礼品，活动火热进行中</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <footer id=\"footer\">\n            <p>© 2024 阳光葵花 | 客服热线：400-888-8888</p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"
